rows.label: qev087605_MSG0001
rows.name:
Medicine, eh? And it's organic stuff you're looking for,
right? Not something to treat a mimeosome?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087605_MSG0002
rows.name:
Well, I can sell you one of the med kits I make.
If you need five, that comes to 100,000 credits.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087605_SEL0011
rows.name: Buy five med kits for 100,000 credits.

rows.label: qev087605_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Jeffery that you changed your mind.

rows.label: qev087605_MSG0003
rows.name:
Here you are. I'm happy to hear they'll go toward
helping people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087605_MSG0004
rows.name:
Yeah, I don't really blame you at that price.
Unfortunately, the only substances out there that work
against Miran pathogens are rare—which means pricey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087605_MSG0005
rows.name:
Er...this isn't quite enough. And look, I know these are
expensive, but the only substances that can combat
Miran pathogens are rare—which means pricey.[ST:wait ]
